<snippet name="obsidianGrotto" scripts="meta/markerDivScript.js">

<div class="panelFull absoluteAlign hidden" identifier="machine">
    <p>An obsidian switch gleams prominently beneath a black screen.</p>

    <div class="machineScreen">
        <label for="coordinates">NODE ID</label>
        <input name="coordinates" type="number" step="1"/>
    </div>

    <p><a class="activateLink" location="obsidianGrotto">Pull switch.</a></p>

    <div class="successfulActivation hidden">
        <p>Light flashes. A coruscating rip in the fabric of spacetime opens before you.</p>

        <p><a class="successfulActivationLink">Enter.</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="unsuccessfulActivation hidden">
        <p>Click. Nothing happens.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="absoluteAlign topHalf">
</div>
<div class="absoluteAlign bottomHalf blackBg">
    <h3 class="roomName">Obsidian Grotto</h3>

    <p>A small cave of smooth black stone. It feels dangerously hot, a temperature that would burn if you could burn. The <a class="panelOpener" identifier="machine">apparatus</a> in the center is wreathed with a frenzy of crackling embers that spark on the metal.</p>

    <p>An exit to the [[east|moltenPumps]] leads to a hissing, crackling field of sulfur, with a bright line of fire on the horizon.</p>
</div>
</snippet>

<snippet name="moltenPumps" scripts="meta/markerDivScript.js">

<div class="absoluteAlign topHalf">
</div>
<div class="absoluteAlign bottomHalf blackBg">
    <h3 class="roomName">Molten Pumps</h3>

    <p>Searing heat fills the air. Before you is an ocean of perpetual fire, incandescent. Instead of a sandy beach, the shore is a flat plain of hissing sulfur, glittering with red embers. The ocean feeds into a conglomeration of machines, tubes and pipes harvesting a constant stream of red-hot liquid from the vehemently flaming tide.</p>

    <p>[[East|harvestMechanism2052A]] takes you along the shore, towards a bronze tower that vents occasional bursts of steam. To the [[south|brimstoneFields]], the rest of the beach is obscured by waveing heat and sparkling red embers. To the [[west|obsidianGrotto]] is a small cave, set into towering obsidian cliffs that block off the rest of the shore.</p>
</div>
</snippet>

